                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#99ra">99ra</locus>:This book is of gʷäytana Gabra
                              Māryām, his father's name is Mazgaba Śǝllāse, his mother name is
                              Walatta Māryām, his wife name is [Wä]lättä Hāymānot, his children
                               Walatta Michael, priest Gabra Ṣādǝqān, Gabra Krǝstos, Gabra Madḫǝn,
                              Gabra Yoḥannǝs. He has bought it with his money so that it might be
                              his guide to the Kingdom of Heaven, and donated it to the tabot of St
                              Michael Bäʾatti.</quote>
